profile_positions.description:
Participate in the product management process as an advisory member of the Change Control Board; 
Process and domain analysis, requirements definition and management, definition studies, impact analysis, design, test, document, present and &quot;sell&quot; standard functionality for the ERP solution Isah(-7); 
Manage and participate in research and development projects;
Presales consultancy;
Implement Isah(-7) - Service and Objects modules - at customers;
Design and implement organisational changes like Iterative Application Development (IAD) and implement CaliberRM for requirements management.

Specific research and development projects are: Service and maintenance (module), Objects (module), CRM, Cost based invoicing, Replication, Usability &amp; navigation (gui, user specific menu's, go to - cross links between related forms).
